{
  "id": "69e347d99b8369bc914bed40",
  "title": "中年やコミュ障が気持ちよく読めるマンガやラノベを探すためのキーワード",
  "created": 1776502747,
  "updated": 1776503492,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e347d99b8369bc914bed40",
      "text": "中年やコミュ障が気持ちよく読めるマンガやラノベを探すためのキーワード",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502747,
      "updated": 1776502844
    },
    {
      "id": "69e347d9000000000043d849",
      "text": "なろう系寄りの読者？が気持ちよく読める作品を探すキーワードを集めたい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502747,
      "updated": 1776502849
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34843000000000043d857",
      "text": " タイトルは仮、もっと良さそうなのあったら変えて",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502852,
      "updated": 1776502892
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34845000000000043d858",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502855,
      "updated": 1776502884
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34812000000000043d855",
      "text": "キーワード：",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502803,
      "updated": 1776502807
    },
    {
      "id": "69e347f0000000000043d84c",
      "text": "\t俺",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502769,
      "updated": 1776502770
    },
    {
      "id": "69e347f1000000000043d84d",
      "text": "\t隣",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502770,
      "updated": 1776502772
    },
    {
      "id": "69e347f2000000000043d84e",
      "text": "\t冒険者",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502772,
      "updated": 1776502774
    },
    {
      "id": "69e347f4000000000043d84f",
      "text": "\tアラフォー",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502774,
      "updated": 1776502775
    },
    {
      "id": "69e347f6000000000043d850",
      "text": "\tアラサー",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502775,
      "updated": 1776502776
    },
    {
      "id": "69e347f7000000000043d851",
      "text": "\tSランク",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502776,
      "updated": 1776502782
    },
    {
      "id": "69e347fd000000000043d852",
      "text": "\tギルド",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502782,
      "updated": 1776502785
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34800000000000043d853",
      "text": "\t竜（またはドラゴン）",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502785,
      "updated": 1776502796
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34802000000000043d854",
      "text": "\t孤児院",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502787,
      "updated": 1776502914
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34881000000000043d85a",
      "text": "\tスライム",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776502914,
      "updated": 1776503444
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34a9400000000006ecb3f",
      "text": "\tテイマー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776503444,
      "updated": 1776503450
    },
    {
      "id": "69e347da000000000043d84a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776502748,
      "updated": 1776502748
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34a0e00000000006ecb3b",
      "text": "文字通りキーワードが欲しいのか、作品を探す方法が欲しいのか[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776503310,
      "updated": 1776503492
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34a3f00000000006ecb3d",
      "text": "\tなろうの作品を適当に読んで「この作品を読んでいる人は他にもこの作品を読んでいます」から辿っていくほうが気持ち良い作品を辿っていけるような",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776503360,
      "updated": 1776503409
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34a7900000000006ecb3e",
      "text": "\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776503417,
      "updated": 1776503417
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34a2300000000006ecb3c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776503331,
      "updated": 1776503331
    }
  ]
}